<title>USA: IA Corp sees Q2 results below expectations.</title>
<headline>IA Corp sees Q2 results below expectations.</headline>
<dateline>EMERYVILLE, Calif. 1997-07-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>IA Corp said Friday its expects to report lower-than-expected second quarter sales and revenues, due to weak results from RemitVision, its second generation financial services software.</p>
<p>The company said it expects to report a second quarter loss between $1 million and $1.2 million, or $0.09 and $0.11 per share, on revenues between $4.2 million and $4.5 million.  </p>
<p>Analyst have been forecasting second quarter earnings of $0.01 per share, according to First Call.</p>
